N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 202.5 - Acceptance

State Regulations

Any person selected by the commissioner as a committee
member shall qualify by filing a written acceptance with the commissioner
within 15 days after being notified of such selection. Notes
